title: RNA editing report website
text:
To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.




flowchart TB
  
 
  
  A[(Raw data)] --- t1(cleaning notebook) 
  t1 --> B[(Cleaned data)]
  B --- t2(COTAN analysis src)  --> C[(COTAN obj)]
  
  C --- t3(COTAN clustering src) --> D[(Clustered COTAN obj)] 
  
  B --- t4(Seurat analysis src) --> E[(Seurat obj)]
  
  E --- t3
  
  t3 --> CD[(Seurat obj with COTAN cl.)]
  
  CD --> t5(Data exploration + Markers +cluster identification notebook) 
  
  D --> t5
  
  t5 --> G[(Seurat obj with cell id)]
  t5 --> H[(COTAN obj with cell id)]
  
  G -->  t6(Exploration & Conclusion notebook) 
  H --> t6
  
  
  classDef src fill:#66cc33;
  classDef notebook fill:#cc99ff;
  
  class t1,t5,t6 notebook;
  class t2,t3,t4 src;
